('SEO in the Age of AI: How to Win When LLMs Answer Instead of Google', 'seo-age-of-ai-llm-answers', 'SEO Strategy', 'Generative Engine Optimisation explained for B2B decision makers', 'Search is changing. AI assistants now answer questions directly. Here is how to ensure your brand is the one they cite.', '', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1432888498266-38ffec3eaf0a?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800', 'SEO', 'SEO, GEO, AI search, LLM, content strategy', 'Digi Pexel Team', 'AI SEO Specialists', '7 min read', 'published', '[{\"id\":\"s1\",\"type\":\"overview\",\"title\":\"The Zero-Click Revolution\",\"content\":\"Over 40% of Google searches now end without a click. AI assistants like ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini answer questions directly from cited sources. If your brand is not one of those sources, you are invisible to an entire generation of buyers.\",\"points\":[\"40%+ of searches end without a click\",\"AI assistants cite 3-5 sources per answer\",\"B2B buyers use AI tools for research before contacting vendors\"]},{\"id\":\"s2\",\"type\":\"challenge\",\"title\":\"Why Traditional SEO Is Not Enough\",\"content\":\"Classic on-page SEO and backlinks still matter, but they do not guarantee AI citation. LLMs are trained on specific datasets and use retrieval-augmented generation to pull live web content. Different signals drive AI visibility.\",\"points\":[\"Keyword density does not drive LLM citations\",\"Backlink authority is a weak signal for AI answers\",\"Structured, entity-rich content outperforms thin pages\"]},{\"id\":\"s3\",\"type\":\"solution\",\"title\":\"Generative Engine Optimisation (GEO)\",\"content\":\"GEO is the practice of optimising content so AI assistants cite your brand in their answers. It combines entity-building, structured content, and authoritative sourcing.\",\"points\":[\"Build topical authority through entity mapping\",\"Use schema markup to signal structured facts\",\"Publish comprehensive pillar content that LLMs can summarise\",\"Earn citations from high-authority sources in your niche\"]},{\"id\":\"s4\",\"type\":\"mid_cta\",\"cta_text\":\"Want an AI visibility audit for your brand?\",\"cta_label\":\"Book a Free Strategy Call\"}]', 1, '2025-04-02')");

